page.title: 11Biography-Faversham Child
page.content:
{A Day In the life of Susan Leadbeater
My name is Susan Leadbeater,I am 8 years of age. I have three brothers older than me. On Sunday,21st. July 1985 I got up and read a comic,called the Beano. Then I went downstairs to watch the television. I watched "Fang-Face". It was about four teenagers one who changes into a WEREWOLF when he sees the moon and changes back when he sees the sun. After "Fang-Face" I had my breakfast,after which I got dressed into my pink dress. I then went out to see my friend Amy Poole who lives at Upper St. Annes. We both live in Faversham. {Susan Leadbeater
